item.description:
Happy Year of Dragon! Come to sing and play with friends to celebrate Chinese New Year this year in Boston Chinatown.

8:15pm-11:00pm Karaoke at Goldenleaf in a private room. Plan to bring $15-$20 for Karaoke room rental and additional money for any drinks/snacks you wish to order.

We'll need to RSVP responsibly as we'll need to make reservations for the private Karaoke room. http://glkaraokeboston.com/
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the Chinese Language Meetup Group

group.name: The Boston Mandarin Chinese Language Meetup Group
